{"tid":1263181,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"71升旗唱咩歌好？","createTime":"2019-06-28T04:53:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-28T04:57:07.000Z","uid":264536,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5bfcc3fd335e42808fb920893a789bcd550e05ba","tid":1263181,"uid":264536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T04:53:58.000Z","msg":"據聞唔會金紫荊升而入會展，不過改變地點並唔改變我哋應該要做咩，不如諗下可以唱咩歌？<br />\n我有個諗法：<br />\n義勇軍進行曲由前奏起共43秒<br />\nDo you hear the people sing (跟電影版公祭嗰陣嘅version）由第一句（個do字）起第44秒入副歌<br />\n佢哋一唱完嗰陣我哋大大力轟落去都幾正<br />\n另<br />\n其實照唱國歌，將中華民族改做香港民族（呢4隻字用廣東話唱都啱音），都幾頂癮<br />\n<br />\n初次開po多多指點"},{"pid":"a524e6aba42e568c0b2c0f206ff8d407d2a46197","tid":1263181,"uid":34676,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T04:55:17.000Z","msg":"唔好做埋d小學雞野，完。"},{"pid":"9e1a0235e9fdddc99eee6a9a5c8918455e4778c8","tid":1263181,"uid":169154,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T04:56:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">起底&gt;BLOCK&gt;上一頁</span></span>"},{"pid":"6c40631fdd0ff45873ee62758b9f8d82b2ffd43d","tid":1263181,"uid":153722,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T04:57:07.000Z","msg":"唱其他歌冇問題<br />\n唔好改首國歌"}]}